const body = live && deps.eventBus
  ? await collectReplayAndLiveEvents({ runId: id, replay: events, eventBus: deps.eventBus, stopAfter })
  : events.map(formatSseEvent).join("");
```
Adapt to current code and tests. Be careful: if stopAfter is invalid/NaN, do not hang a request indefinitely in tests; use conservative parsing if needed while preserving spec.
